# E2E harness — ignore generated artifacts. Golden cassettes ARE committed
# (they are evidence; structural diffs against them are how we detect
# regressions). Replays, run logs, and node_modules are not.

node_modules/
.tmp/
.tsbuild/
cassettes/replays/
*.log

# Allow committed golden cassettes.
!cassettes/golden/
!cassettes/golden/**

# Allow committed seed-corpus traces. These are recorded-trace
# regression anchors (live captures pinned to the repo so offline tests
# can re-validate the structural shape without re-spending the API
# budget). See `_phase-a-trace.unit.spec.ts` and
# claude-workflow-plugin-l1r.7. Add new traces deliberately; they
# document a moment-in-time live evidence and must not churn.
!cassettes/seed/
!cassettes/seed/**
